CatDescriptText: image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 11, 1950, pg. 1. Headline reads: "First Baptist Church, Penn Township, Is Scene Of Ceremony Uniting Miss Gaines, Mr. Hollinger"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of bride Arlene Allen Gaines Hollinger wearing satin wedding gown with sweetheart neckline and lace trimmed veil, holding prayer books with ribbons and orange blossoms, posed in front of dark velvet curtain, in First Baptist Church, Penn Township
